g**\n\nI'm thinking about whether the parent should be included for the xml-resolver. It seems it might not be necessary. I wonder if I need to handle the Class#newInstance reflection call within the test itself, maybe to ensure I add coverage? But I'm not targeting it specifically. Also, can I catch ReflectiveOperationException? The method throws generic Exception, which adds some uncertainty.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0aa938860c6eeb2d0169f59166db288193876996f662821eb8\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp9ZF-9zwlvBzQSK-yIzfDgkPfcHb9KrN3nNfyxZx7J5BevzKQ_PFREc452IkEhJYDQaKIp6Hs9GrB3XvATB-Pw_TcdiqGuPEesYeUhKq6KiVkALxSb427l7Y3lJlWk4zAyqAHqt-R1Ij8F_YfviqMi6IC-woZkrpMXWNurJd_7WeAXkKbAQxNIxHBW7PERAPCiThrHHmx32ZsW70S-FxP74KeUSQwRDB314de8GhGuFGchEDd3OGEgUb910yHEpBTL6ZLUEJnhGZ1iDmuVaQyufmxqO9tVNPBKBc4FJygMfQqMHTJu_lhud517rjp010mumOa4Kb05CRdgPP1WP8hxEJ54EyA9lJqDuXzfKIsvhelk8GHkztCi4-hi33K1j6P3vpnwmi238sNOxnAXF5ZJY9QD8i-dy_i5Fdf7rStw6VENGaBv1thw5yVU_E3G_QX4t9mlNkauqJaHkMMb0XcYBVe0FnwlJ5m5LE-egjy7vOr9xNXPr_OBs3m6sX0vvPNezuWzvXyXmVyiV4oMtmG_hk_IywxzafFdKw80pQGrQ70Xj2lkTdjJQYEakphUVrAg7KQonQ-TH3FyLl9FuES53yAOz3us6x4ZmT2ZUzJe8E0peFFa2YKblREpvcYDWSDmQzDbKiKvhVcAo89rGK-7N2JOZrKKgABva6x2ODufY_uld7DlXvPUAlfl8_ABYiD4VqjiKXEj6ozruNyJYU8UQVTZWOiRlUH8qS-qTpKTH6L6bkqqil0FgT9IbB1htpv8oNbB-ZJ08gTdFOpbijnge_4cAo6-wAt4fAjTu7t-c-Z7DHhe76ezJON1lxptFnFaX4JKZpT5ETczK5ziPXiT35pIwVr9qOYYY1ZTwrjw9tQqrSDNkaGgcpj2F2vtBngPbftLMnEjF4tt_rfYWL9QsfrzxxxExB2LJpm7EoQ8xt1ymHcPsvO5dDgjboa5ECq807OtJjTxo79SpwcoXplv0DyqG7sFrxtNXvQf2O_tG8DSL3MpJBQjJk6_PHnBgaFQFyiCkd2DjnqO0eZJqIqMpQ9SfTEBwg0Nf8jc-o_5gOjZ8CM4vWhZvcqdy9pvVI64kQx03UBmeqyNi4Wl6-r4T7w903vJRxmGsQDurO4Bd6tQvnwddjVLVhSUNL1BYgxCDX3Vz3q_oZSazhTOnqYiISsJ2tqlwqZDXxOlrBO1A65Sr0GIK-SBiQUMNc31aQU2W07VqprRPgP_WhbYRBkPf8Ryq08BKgyC--udWzN0ng7lDR1jO_vNYImhfjN3hYJGtUXoUuh4LsuzrVWZAML3WbIdc6cTikzGivpq7qvSwnaEBX_xJw9cXRvjphG__5T-BaOIfm6xJTX48SEMIiPkBQAXR8-HUGc67ctpSy6Y5rQrKtURT-frUb1REPEcNDEjvVhFMi0BgIKjWu00pCx98V-9QJqrfC8FgTDAQ2uwJDvWwZ0D